metadata.title: FIGURE 9 in Revision of the family Chasmocarcinidae Serène, 1964 (Crustacea, Brachyura, Goneplacoidea)
metadata.description: FIGURE 9. Overall dorsal view, chela and buccal area of Chasmocarcinops gelasimoides. A, B, Andaman Sea: male (after Alcock 1899a: pl. 62 fig. 3, 3a); C, D, Andaman Sea: female (after Alcock 1899a: pl. 62 fig. 2, 2a); E, Andaman Sea: male 8.8 × 9.5 mm (PMBC 16849); F, Andaman Sea: female 11.5 × 12.4 mm (PMBC 16894); G, Singapore: male 9.5 × 10.3 mm (ZRC 2000.1341); H, Singapore: female 9.3 × 10.6 mm (ZRC 2013.1411).
